data.description:
BRAND NEW HOME!! READY TO MOVE-IN!! BEAUTIFUL DESIGNER UPGRADES! Stunning brand-new construction home featuring 3 bedrooms/2 baths. This exquisite home offers an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings. Modern light fixtures throughout. The kitchen features ample counter space, an island, quartz countertops, subway tile backsplash, 42" wood cabinets, brand-new stainless-steel appliances and a generous pantry space. Beautiful ceramic tile floors in wet areas and modern water-resistant laminate flooring throughout. Master bedroom is overlooking the rear patio, a barn door entry to the master bathroom with dual-sink quartz vanity tops, a beautiful shower and a spacious walk-in closet. Enjoy the big backyard and covered lanai to entertain family and friends. It also features an interior laundry room, 2 car garage, brand new wood fenced and much more. Close to supermarkets, schools, and major roads. DEFINITELY A MUST SEE!

Renters: pays for water, garbage, utilities.
